<body>
    <h1>Leave Of Absence (LOA) (Associate) (Use Case=E2=80=93 UC06)</h1>
    <div class=3D"Section1">
        <h3 id=3D"LeaveOfAbsence(LOA)(Associate)(UseCase=E2=80=93UC06)-Leav=
eOfAbsenceworkflow">Leave Of Absence workflow</h3>
<p>Table-22</p>
<div class=3D"table-wrap">
<table data-table-width=3D"1800" data-layout=3D"default" data-local-id=3D"9=
f8fcd3f-a709-41c6-9699-cdbde5d37dbb" class=3D"confluenceTable">
<colgroup>
<col style=3D"width: 243.0px;">
<col style=3D"width: 1556.0px;">
</colgroup>
<tbody>
<tr>
<td data-highlight-colour=3D"#d9e2f3" class=3D"confluenceTd">
<p>Type</p></td>
<td class=3D"confluenceTd">
<p>Leave Of Absence (LOA)&nbsp;</p></td>
</tr>
<tr>
<td data-highlight-colour=3D"#d9e2f3" class=3D"confluenceTd">
<p>Description</p></td>
<td class=3D"confluenceTd">
<p>The LOA use case describes the Leave Of Absence process for user identit=
ies in SailPoint IIQ. SailPoint will automatically disable access privilege=
s in SailPoint and the associated downstream systems.&nbsp;</p></td>
</tr>
<tr>
<td data-highlight-colour=3D"#d9e2f3" class=3D"confluenceTd">
<p>List of Attributes&nbsp;</p></td>
<td class=3D"confluenceTd">
<p>The following set of attributes represent the tentative set of users=E2=
=80=99 attributes which will be used in the process flow. The final set of =
source and target attributes will be finalized in the solution design docum=
ent.</p>
<ol start=3D"1">
<li>
<p>First Name&nbsp;</p></li>
<li>
<p>Last Name&nbsp;</p></li>
<li>
<p>Person Number&nbsp;</p></li>
<li>
<p>Assignment Status&nbsp;</p></li>
<li>
<p>System Worker Type&nbsp;</p></li>
<li>
<p>Action Name&nbsp;</p></li>
<li>
<p>Start Date</p></li>
<li>
<p>Hire Date&nbsp;</p></li>
<li>
<p>Effective Date&nbsp;</p></li>
<li>
<p>Department&nbsp;</p></li>
<li>
<p>Position&nbsp;</p></li>
<li>
<p>Location&nbsp;</p></li>
<li>
<p>Termination date&nbsp;</p></li>
<li>
<p>Ministry</p></li>
<li>
<p>Effective Start Date</p></li>
</ol>
<p></p>
<p>Refer Appendix =E2=80=9C<a class=3D"external-link" href=3D"https://drive=
.google.com/drive/folders/17u4oN4VdyLijziIcn8PMSlUxT5HS_LW0" rel=3D"nofollo=
w"><u>Source and Target Attribute Mapping</u></a>=E2=80=9D for complete lis=
t of attribute mapping.</p></td>
</tr>
<tr>
<td data-highlight-colour=3D"#d9e2f3" class=3D"confluenceTd">
<p>Pre-Conditions</p></td>
<td class=3D"confluenceTd">
<p>User is already present in SailPoint IdentityIQ with existing accounts a=
nd access details.</p></td>
</tr>
<tr>
<td data-highlight-colour=3D"#d9e2f3" class=3D"confluenceTd">
<p>Trigger</p></td>
<td class=3D"confluenceTd">
<p>When following conditions are true:</p>
<ol start=3D"1">
<li>
<p>The <strong>Assignment Effective Start Date</strong> attribute value sho=
uld be less than or equal to current date.</p></li>
<li>
<p>=E2=80=98<strong>Assignment status</strong>=E2=80=99 attribute should be=
 equal to '<strong>Leave Of Absence - Payroll Eligible</strong>=E2=80=99 / =
=E2=80=98<strong>Active - Payroll Eligible</strong>=E2=80=99.</p></li>
<li>
<p>=E2=80=98<strong>System Worker Type</strong>=E2=80=99 attribute should b=
e equal to =E2=80=98<strong>Associate</strong>=E2=80=99.</p></li>
<li>
<p>=E2=80=98<strong>Action Name</strong>=E2=80=99 attributes value should e=
qual to =E2=80=98<strong>Leave Of Absence</strong>=E2=80=99/ =E2=80=99<stro=
ng>Return from Leave of Absence</strong>=E2=80=99.</p></li>
</ol></td>
</tr>
<tr>
<td data-highlight-colour=3D"#d9e2f3" class=3D"confluenceTd">
<p>Basic Flow</p></td>
<td class=3D"confluenceTd">
<ol start=3D"1">
<li>
<p>Oracle HR will send the Effective Date to SailPoint IdentityIQ.</p></li>
<li>
<p>The Assignment Effective Start Date attribute value should be less than =
or equal to current date.</p></li>
<li>
<p>User accounts will be disabled in SailPoint IdentityIQ.</p></li>
<li>
<p>SailPoint IdentityIQ will remove user=E2=80=99s Active Directory groups =
and security groups, disable other downstream application accounts except A=
ctive Directory and GSuite.</p></li>
<li>
<p>User=E2=80=99s Active Directory account without group membership self-se=
rvice access on Oracle ERP Cloud and GSuite account remains active.</p></li=
>
</ol></td>
</tr>
<tr>
<td data-highlight-colour=3D"#d9e2f3" class=3D"confluenceTd">
<p>List of downstream applications</p></td>
<td class=3D"confluenceTd">
<p>Active Directory, Azure, GSuite, ServiceNow, Oracle ERP Cloud, Oracle EP=
M Cloud, OCI.</p></td>
</tr>
<tr>
<td data-highlight-colour=3D"#d9e2f3" class=3D"confluenceTd">
<p>Acceptance criteria</p></td>
<td class=3D"confluenceTd">
<ul>
<li>
<p>User=E2=80=99s group membership for Active Directory groups is removed b=
ut the account is left active.</p></li>
<li>
<p>User=E2=80=99s Oracle ERP Cloud account with self-service access and GSu=
ite accounts remains active.</p></li>
<li>
<p>User=E2=80=99s accounts for other downstream applications are disabled.<=
/p></li>
</ul></td>
</tr>
<tr>
<td data-highlight-colour=3D"#d9e2f3" class=3D"confluenceTd">
<p>Error handling</p></td>
<td class=3D"confluenceTd">
<p>A ServiceNow ticket will be created and assigned to the Ascension Health=
 Alliance SailPoint IIQ support team.</p></td>
</tr>
<tr>
<td data-highlight-colour=3D"#d9e2f3" class=3D"confluenceTd">
<p>Persona / Actors</p></td>
<td class=3D"confluenceTd">
<p>Automated Process</p></td>
</tr>
</tbody>
</table>
</div>
<p></p>
<p><strong>Dependency:</strong></p>
<div class=3D"table-wrap">
<table data-table-width=3D"903" data-layout=3D"center" data-local-id=3D"58e=
b8119-01b5-431a-bb37-e55fe2da5ed3" class=3D"confluenceTable">
<colgroup>
<col style=3D"width: 58.0px;">
<col style=3D"width: 156.0px;">
<col style=3D"width: 689.0px;">
</colgroup>
<tbody>
<tr>
<td data-highlight-colour=3D"#d4deec" class=3D"confluenceTd">
<p>S. no</p></td>
<td data-highlight-colour=3D"#d4deec" class=3D"confluenceTd">
<p>Dependency</p></td>
<td data-highlight-colour=3D"#d4deec" class=3D"confluenceTd">
<p>Point of contact for answers</p></td>
</tr>
<tr>
<td class=3D"confluenceTd">
<p>1</p></td>
<td class=3D"confluenceTd">
<p>List of attributes</p></td>
<td class=3D"confluenceTd">
<p>Oracle HCM Cloud application team to send the final set of attributes ma=
pping</p></td>
</tr>
<tr>
<td class=3D"confluenceTd">
<p>2</p></td>
<td class=3D"confluenceTd">
<p>Trigger</p></td>
<td class=3D"confluenceTd">
<p>Oracle HCM Cloud application team to finalize the attributes and its val=
ues required for trigger</p></td>
</tr>
<tr>
<td class=3D"confluenceTd">
<p>3</p></td>
<td class=3D"confluenceTd">
<p>Basic Flow</p></td>
<td class=3D"confluenceTd">
<p>Oracle HCM Cloud application team to finalize the attributes and its val=
ues required in the Basic Flow</p></td>
</tr>
</tbody>
</table>
</div>
